This is a simple sender-receiver example in ROS.
This repository contains the three packages chatter_msgs, chatter_sender
and chatter_receiver. It mainly serves as a simple case study for the
meta-ros layer.

MAINTAINER
  Lukas Bulwahn, BMW Car IT GmbH <lukas.bulwahn@oss.bmw-carit.de>

AUTHORS
